Manipulao

pop_df <- df_ibge %>%
  mutate(
    bairro = str_remove(bairro, " \\- Joo Pessoa \\(PB\\)"),
    renda = str_replace_all(renda, "salrio mnimo|salrios mnimos", "SM"),
    valor = replace_na(valor, 0)
  )
pop_df <- pop_df %>%
  mutate(
    renda = fct_collapse(
      renda,
      "At 1/2 SM" = c(
        "At 1/4 de SM",
        "Mais de 1/4 a 1/2 SM"
      ),
      "Mais de 10 SM" = c(
        "Mais de 10 a 15 SM",
        "Mais de 15 a 20 SM",
        "Mais de 20 a 30 SM",
        "Mais de 30 SM"
      )
    )
  )
pop_df <- pop_df %>%
  mutate(
    racial = fct_relevel(
      racial,
      "Branca", "Parda", "Preta", "Indgena", "Amarela"
    ),
    renda = fct_relevel(
      renda,
      "At 1/2 SM", "Mais de 1/2 a 1 SM",
      "Mais de 1 a 2 SM", "Mais de 2 a 3 SM",
      "Mais de 3 a 5 SM", "Mais de 5 a 10 SM",
      "Mais de 10 SM", "Sem rendimento"
    )
  ) %>%
  group_by(bairro, racial, renda) %>%
  summarize(valor = sum(valor), .groups = "drop")
filter(pop_df, bairro == "Mangabeira", racial == "Preta")

Explorao

i)

Desagrupamento automtico com tidyr::pivot_wider()

renda_vs_racial <- pop_df %>%
  group_by(racial, renda) %>%
  summarize(valor = sum(valor), .groups = "drop_last") %>%
  mutate(valor = valor / last(valor)) %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = racial, values_from = valor)

get_split <- function(y, x) {
  x <- enquo(x)
  y %>%
    select(bairro, !!x, valor) %>%
    group_by(bairro, !!x) %>%
    summarize(valor = sum(valor), .groups = "drop") %>%
    pivot_wider(names_from = !!x, values_from = valor) %>%
    janitor::clean_names()
}
sf_ibge <- geobr::read_neighborhood(year = 2010) %>%
  filter(code_muni == 2507507)

ii)

branq <- pop_df %>%
  get_split(racial) %>%
  mutate(branca = branca / total) %>%
  select(bairro, branca)
plot_branq <- branq %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = branca)) +
  geom_histogram(aes(y = ..density..)) +
  geom_density()

iii)

k_rendim <- pop_df %>%
  get_split(renda) %>%
  mutate_if(
    is.numeric,
    ~ .x / (total - sem_rendimento)
  )
set.seed(321)

k_rendim <- k_rendim %>%
  mutate(
    cluster = select(., contains("_sm")) %>%
      kmeans(centers = 3) %>%
      .$cluster %>%
      as_factor()
  ) %>%
  select(bairro, cluster)
plot_rendim <- k_rendim %>%
  mutate(bairro = str_to_title(bairro)) %>%
  inner_join(sf_ibge, by = c("bairro" = "name_neighborhood")) %>%
  ggplot(aes(geometry = geom, fill = cluster)) +
  geom_sf(alpha = .6, color = "white")

Resultados

pred_logit <- k_rendim %>%
  inner_join(branq, by = "bairro") %>%
  mutate(
    pred = MASS::polr(cluster ~ branca) %>%
      predict(),
    acc = ifelse(cluster == pred, 1, 0) %>%
      as_factor()
  )

pred_logit %>%
  filter(acc == 1) %>%
  nrow()
## [1] 51
plot_final <- pred_logit %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = branca, y = cluster)) +
  geom_boxplot(aes(fill = cluster)) +
  geom_jitter(aes(color = acc), height = .3)
